name: Keilah Kang Killian
description:
Keilah Kang Killian is a model, brand ambassador, and Instagram personality that lives in North Carolina.

During the tests, the TI proved to be very good, very flexible and "obedient". But I highly recommend reduced weight. For example, "(kel1ah:0.9)" works fine in most cases.

And please add "child, childish" to your negative prompt.

I hope someone likes this TI. As always, I will be happy to receive any review or feedback
